  "text": "And the third question I have here is could you give examples of bodily polarity. I am Ra. Within the body there are many polarities which relate to the balancing of the energy centers of the various bodies of the unmanifested entity. It is well to explore these polarities for work in healing. Each entity is of, of course, a potential, a polarized portion of an other self.",
